19:16.381 --> 19:21.451
But then you did say that there's a battleground in between where you can test, where you kind of go after this.

19:21.611 --> 19:23.495
You gave me a quote on that, which I thought was very good.

19:23.535 --> 19:24.838
I'd love to have it on tape.

19:24.858 --> 19:25.739
I don't remember what it was.

19:25.860 --> 19:26.842
It was kind of like that.

19:27.102 --> 19:28.645
We were talking about something like that.

19:29.080 --> 19:39.716
