19:40.497 --> 19:43.141
And Subby's and Christie's role is defined.

19:43.521 --> 19:46.065
The role of their book department is not defined by the book department.

19:46.085 --> 19:47.267
I think it's really what it comes down to.

19:47.287 --> 19:53.075
The role of the book department is defined as being a department in a major international enterprise.

19:53.095 --> 19:56.961
