19:57.751 --> 20:10.164
Given any particular item, with some exception, minor exception, given any particular item, we will get the same price, and it will sell to the same person, because there's only so many customers.

20:10.244 --> 20:17.773
Again, that's not 100% true, but by and large, you've got the same people selling to the same people.

20:18.854 --> 20:22.758
You've got the same buyers, the same sellers, and they've got a choice of three houses.

20:23.158 --> 20:24.720
Absolutely.

